Author: scaredyk4t
Text: Omfg...a good friend of mine keeps so many snacks and we will cook meals together and I will eat the veggie version. I don’t mind the veg version and actually prefer it...but the other day when she was grilling that burger...I was so tempted to say fuck it GIVE ME THE DAMN BURGER! even tho normally meat and the meat “juices” gross me tf out...
